function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(VGN_CONV_02_POST_CHURCH, idActor)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_EFFIGY, false)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_CHILD1, ID_RUNTO, "NPC_RUN", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_CHILD1, 2)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_CHILD1)
end
